gy. Thanks to the insensitivity of the\nvelocity divergence to bias, its PDF can be used to obtain unbiased constraints\non the growth of structures ($\\sigma_8$,f) or it can be combined with the\ngalaxy density PDF to extract bias parameters.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 30 Nov 2016 21:00:04 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 18 May 2017 13:35:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-08-03"}
