 be derived when attack time distributions are\nknown.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 1 Dec 2016 01:43:24 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 2 Dec 2016 18:26:18 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-12-05"}
